Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php-vitexsoftware-multiflexi-core, multiflexi-cli (>= 2.2.0), php-symfony-mailer
Description: MultiFlexi Mail credential prototype
 SMTP mail credential prototype for MultiFlexi core.
 Provides the CredentialProtoType class that defines Mailer DSN
 and sender address configuration fields using Symfony Mailer.

Package: multiflexi-mail-ui
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, multiflexi-mail (= ${binary:Version}), multiflexi-web
Description: MultiFlexi Mail UI components
 Mail connection dialog for MultiFlexi web interface.
 Tests SMTP connectivity, displays server capabilities (EHLO),
 and sends test messages via Symfony Mailer.
